Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed \Na pirate alliance with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But caught up in the current \Nking Doflamingo's agenda,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthey were trapped along with the entire island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll pay 100 million berries \Nfor each star rating!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 million berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On top of that, he put prices on \Nthe heads of Luffy and 11 others,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now they're being hunted \Nby all the citizens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with the Straw Hats fighting \Nthe Don Quixote Family fiercely,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Law are heading \Nto the Royal Palace!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar is awake now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sent chills down my spine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I realized Robin had been \Nturned into a toy, too, earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even realize\NI had forgotten about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Sugar touches Luffy,\NI'll forget about him like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend disappears\Nand you won't even know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no option left now!\NI'll shoot her from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the position you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our bond can't be broken\Neven if anyone tries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Luffy ever calls for my help,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:05:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter where I am in the world,\NI'll be there - forget my position!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge, Farul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a powerful jaw!\NIt crushed his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die on me, Farul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they invincible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pop Baller!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! My Yellow Cubs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca, take the key to the Sunflower Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cien Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Tra-guy-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\NYou guys are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got away...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's just one little tramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know she can't do anything\Neven if she can get to the Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Tra-guy-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\NAnd Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go now!\NTo the Sunflower Field on the fourth level!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca's waiting for you!\NJust go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Risking Their Lives!\NLuffy is the Trump Card for Victory!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the fourth level! We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! Thank you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yellow Cubs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}san{\i0} and Bartolomeo-{\i1}san{\i0}...\NAre they okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know they are!\NUsoland's friends are strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:07:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\NWe have to go save Princess Mansherry now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to leave you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine! Lucy and the \Nothers will come soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NGo save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!\NRebecca-{\i1}sama{\i0}, you take care, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soldier-san is a brave man{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He will always be by your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father-sama must be\Nsomewhere on this battlefield, too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody made it here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}, let me take this!\N--Crest Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are balls of explosives!\NThey'll explode before you deflect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I don't deserve such praise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartolomeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!! I just saw his Second Gear\Nand Jet Whip up close!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}, just get rid of them\Nand let's move along already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking too much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!\NDon't talk to Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier-bility: Stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!\NYou saved us a lot of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please use it, Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you looking the other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Crest Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...n...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...k...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Thank you! Thank you! Thank...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who has to thank you\Nfor being born!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go straight to the fourth level this way!\NLet's go, Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issho-{\i1}san{\i0}! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! We can't get closer \Nbecause of the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go around either because
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe collapsed buildings are blocking our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flare-Flare Fruit!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The troublesome guy gained \Na troublesome power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you...\NWhat are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Navy admirals are much more powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an odd person.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you wanted to keep us Navy at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will you keep up with the act?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,\NI need people to go easy on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't discriminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not known as No.2 of the Revolutionary Army\Nfor nothing, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm in the position that\Nrequires me to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raging Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raging Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Horizontal gravity?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! This is just what I expected from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This jerk! What is he up to?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an all-or-nothing gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm determined to bet my life on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose your dice,\Nthe game is over before you can even roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Top Executives of our Family are\Nguarding this plateau...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think anyone could reach it\Nbut there was a slight chance, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I've been waiting but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait, Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep them here! Just go, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved horse was harmed\Non this level!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:20:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go farther without\Nvengeance against those jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, dodge! It's the bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not use your barriers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a limit on the size of the barrier...\Nthat I can produce at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I used it up on that staircase!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it helps Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight with you until you're \Nable to use barriers so hang tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These dolls have no delicacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cinco Mano! Spank!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rooster-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...worth risking...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is always\Nthe trump card that leads us to victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mil Fleurs! Gigantesco Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:23:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I won't let you lay a finger on Luffy!\N--That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.07,0:23:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Top Executive, Diamante, \Nlaunches powerful attacks while
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca struggles desperately to hold on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she is finally driven into a corner,\Nmoments from losing her innocent life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when the legendary, undefeated warrior,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros, shows up at the Sunflower Field!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"A Tearful Reunion! Rebecca and Kyros!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.35,0:23:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.80,0:23:50.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
